                                          1313  # partial samples after transitioning into vertical blank. This is easiest if
                                          1314  # the modulo is 0 (do nothing), 1 (reset sample when entering the last visible
                                          1315  # scan line), or 2 (reset sample while in the first blank scan line). For the
                                          1316  # last case there is no solution yet: give a warning.
